---
import TerminalWindow from './TerminalWindow.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 sm:px-8 border-t border-border">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10 reveal">
      No cloud. <span class="text-primary">Direct connection.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="reveal stagger-1">
      <TerminalWindow title="architecture" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <pre class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs leading-relaxed"><span class="text-text-tertiary">┌──────────────┐</span>         <span class="text-text-tertiary">┌───────────────────┐</span>         <span class="text-text-tertiary">┌──────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-primary">Your Phone</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">ws://</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-success">marmy agent</span>      <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">stdin/</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-text-primary">Claude Code</span> <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>
<span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  iOS app      <span class="text-text-tertiary">│ ◄──────► │</span>  Rust daemon       <span class="text-text-tertiary">│ ◄──────► │</span>  (subprocess) <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>
<span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>              <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>         <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">LAN / Tailscale</span>   <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">stdout</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">N sessions</span>  <span class="text-text-tertiary">│</span>
<span class="text-text-tertiary">└──────────────┘</span>         <span class="text-text-tertiary">└───────────────────┘</span>         <span class="text-text-tertiary">└──────────────┘</span></pre>
      </TerminalWindow>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
